Anerlisa Muigai says her husband Ben Pol has released the "most ratchet video ever". His new song, 'Ndio Mbaya', talks about the pain of love and someone who doesn't return the love back. The music video shows different women in dheras, twerking. Taking to Instagram, the businesswoman rubbished it. "A lot of people have been asking me what I think of Ben's new video, "Hiyo Ndio Mbaya". Honestly, I feel its the most ratchet video ever!!" Fans have claimed this is a strategy to drive more people to watch her husband's new project, which is obviously working. She is currently in Tanzania, where she went to visit her husband, and she has been sharing photos of them enjoying a good time together.